Vol / Page: A7
Edition:
Quote: Pingao, a native sandsedge unique to New Zealand, stabilises sand dunes in the coast areas where it grows, by trapping wind-blown sand around its base and in its leaves ands roots. The biggest threats to pingao are beach vehicles and introduced plants.
